{"tid":2047664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"爆被「萬人迷」誘上房 吳啟華忽然道歉：為了好玩好笑","createTime":"2020-06-02T09:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T10:24:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9511b28dffd88e2794b24d24f2a2a7e6b9974bc","tid":2047664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"視帝馬國明同吳啟華等日前喺無綫節目《Tiger&rsquo;s Talk》接受伍詠薇（伍姑娘）同林盛斌（Bob）訪問時，大爆喺大陸拍劇被女星派房號引誘上房，而吳啟華更透露曾有「萬人迷」女星晚晚派房號。正當唔少人食花生估吓究竟女主角係邊個時，竟然引發軒然大波！<br />\n<br />\n不時上大陸工作嘅吳啟華，今早突然喺大陸嘅社交網用簡體字留言道歉：「在一個只談風花雪月的訪談節目，亂講一些偶爾聽來的奇聞往事，其實原意也只是為了好玩好笑！絕無意污名化任何人，也不希望大家胡亂猜測！如果對任何人因為這次事件做成有甚麼不愉快的，小弟在此深表歉意！事實上，昨天助手和我分析今次事件後，我也確實意識到自己的不該和不是！身為公眾人物，言行確實該份外小心！今後一定不會再犯！請大家原諒！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9CU6yNqxjoVwdwsYFQOqoA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDky/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/0ff90130-a499-11ea-9b51-0ade69d1717c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9CU6yNqxjoVwdwsYFQOqoA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDky%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F0ff90130-a499-11ea-9b51-0ade69d1717c&h=933872a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/odHjREUm_s4mNSHCulhh1g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9MzQx/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/48a42550-a499-11ea-b9ae-66f8859a8b08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FodHjREUm_s4mNSHCulhh1g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9MzQx%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2F48a42550-a499-11ea-b9ae-66f8859a8b08&h=04f237e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13dbe1754818da540afa882073626a0287c6c2d0","tid":2047664,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:01:28.0